            <div class="entry-problem"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;">&lt;보기&gt;에서 국가 인권 위원회의 역할로 알맞은 것을 모두 골라 기호를 쓰시오.</p><div class="para0"><table style="border-collapse:collapse;width:275px;margin:3px 3px 3px 3px;" class="itex_example_tb"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; width:5px; height:8pt"></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="2" style="border:none; border-collapse:collapse; width:70px; height:15pt; vertical-align:middle;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:Center;"><span style="font-size:10pt;">&lt;보기&gt;</span></p></td><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; height:8pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; height:5pt"></td><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; height:5pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; width:9pt; height:19pt"></td><td colspan="3" rowspan="1" style="border:none; border-collapse:collapse; height:19pt; vertical-align:middle;"><div class="itex_box_body" data-table-title="보기"><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㄱ. 법이나 제도의 문제점을 찾아 개선을 권고한다.</p></div><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㄴ. 진정을 받아 조사하여 침해된 권리를 구제한다.</p></div><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㄷ. 행정 심판을 통해 불합리한 행정 제도를 개선한다.</p></div><div class="itex_box_element"><p class="para0">ㄹ. 기본권을 침해당한 국민의 요청을 받아 헌법 소원 심판을 실시한다.</p></div></div></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; width:9pt; height:19pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="5" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; height:6pt"></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class="para0" style="text-align:right;"><span data-mathinfo="78,1000,2605,1195;;BOX{~~~~~}" class="itexmath itexboxevt_parent" contenteditable="false" data-latex="\displaystyle  \class{itexboxevt}{} \boxed { \,\, \,\, \,\, \,\, \,\, \mathstrut } "><mjx-container class="MathJax" jax="SVG" role="presentation" style="position: relative;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="4.979ex" height="3.471ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -1017 2200.7 1534" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.17ex;"><defs></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mstyle"><g data-mml-node="mrow" class="itexboxevt"></g><g data-mml-node="menclose"><g transform="translate(267, 0)"><g data-mml-node="mstyle"><g data-mml-node="TeXAtom" data-mjx-texclass="ORD"><g data-mml-node="mstyle"><g data-mml-node="mspace"></g></g><g data-mml-node="mstyle" transform="translate(166.7, 0)"><g data-mml-node="mspace"></g></g><g data-mml-node="mstyle" transform="translate(333.3, 0)"><g data-mml-node="mspace"></g></g><g data-mml-node="mstyle" transform="translate(500, 0)"><g data-mml-node="mspace"></g></g><g data-mml-node="mstyle" transform="translate(666.7, 0)"><g data-mml-node="mspace"></g></g><g data-mml-node="mstyle" transform="translate(833.3, 0)"><g data-mml-node="mspace"></g></g><g data-mml-node="mstyle" transform="translate(1000, 0)"><g data-mml-node="mspace"></g></g><g data-mml-n